      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, it starts up and runs without major issues, though it lacks the refinement of a newer or better-maintained model. You will notice some significant cosmetic wear, including several scratches on the exterior and some staining and wear on the interior upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done, but it definitely shows its age and usage.",
