      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this example offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a truly peerless motorcar.",
