    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s basically a time capsule! It looks and drives exactly like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014totally flawless and pampered its whole life. No scratches, no stories, just pure perfection. I've taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner will be just as thrilled as I\u2019ve been. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
